verbose_text: In anti-mock-transfected DCs, high miR-410-5p level, in contrast to the very low miR-410-3p level, was observed, while significantly increased miR-410-3p level as well as significantly reduced miR-410-5p level were observed in anti-miR-410-5-transfected DCs, indicating that miR-410-5p could downregulate miR-410-3p.
